{"tid":1743455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本土派無限分裂　只因「公眾是白痴」？","createTime":"2019-11-21T08:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T08:16:29.000Z","uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f5aad52dfc350ca902679bc6c31ce2964112e1bd","tid":1743455,"uid":297241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:03:13.000Z","msg":"本土派無限分裂　只因「公眾是白痴」？<br />\n<br />\n近日，立法會議員鄭松泰的一段錄音在網絡流傳，錄音中他表示與青年新政只不過是「扮friend」，又指「公眾係白痴」才以為他們是「本土派」，引起社會熱議。事實上，過去陳雲、黃毓民等「本土派」領袖，政治立場一向搖擺不定，與多個非建制陣營先是稱兄道弟，吸走其支持者後便翻臉不認人，鄭松泰此言只不過是再次顯露其「政治菠蘿雞」的醜態而已。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n過去數年，香港政治經歷巨變，新政團不斷冒起，政黨分裂也成為常態。一些自稱「本土派」的政客不時在網台、面書互相攻訐，甚至不惜互揭私隱，醜態百出，這已然令他們部分的支持者心灰意冷。"},{"pid":"232a4035e9bdafd3e9fb24e0a00565a25c51e17e","tid":1743455,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:04:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一齊入嚟睇致勝關鍵！！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[拒絕分化！]古人一早教我地點贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"9064367315de656ddf8f52b120a283c141f7cc1b","tid":1743455,"uid":58958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/21/133847_67873c57e2ed76affcd7b96707c782a5.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F21%2F133847_67873c57e2ed76affcd7b96707c782a5.jpeg&h=52bdda44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">建制完勝！<br />\n中共萬歲！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"69e4407bc6e3fcba5890be9b89b5a32